                                <textarea name="proof_of_concept" id="proof_of_concept" placeholder="Include any of the following:&#10;&#10;- Working exploit code or payloads&#10;- HTTP requests/responses&#10;- Screenshots or video links&#10;- Tool output (Burp, sqlmap, etc.)&#10;- Any other evidence supporting your report"></textarea>
                            </div>
