                                <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line>
                            </svg>
                            <a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/cheat-sheet/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown cheat sheet</a> • Be careful not to include sensitive data from other users
                        </div>
